        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Easily tackle everyday dry messes in style with Beille’s Modern Dust Pan and Brust Set! Measuring 13 x 8 inches, Beille’s dust pan and brush set is a must have household essentials item that will make quick work of dry messes in the kitchen, laundry room, garage, entryway, bathrooms and more.<br/><br/>The dust pan itself is lightweight and easy to carry between spaces; it comes with a built in TPR rubber edge to keep pan in place and to improve debris collection efficiency. The dust pan brush features a sustainable bamboo handle that ensures a comfortable and ergonomic grip when sweeping. The dust pan brush also boasts non scratch bristles that are soft but dense, easily cleaning up messes with just a few sweeps! And lastly, the top of the dust pan features built in teeth to help remove unwanted materials from the brush.<br/><br/>Beille’s dust pan and brush set both feature built in hanging holes for convenient accessibility when not in use, while the space saving brush and pan easily snap together, helping to keep storage areas, cabinets or closets tidy and organized. The natural bamboo handle and pop of confetti-like design lend a stylish but organic and neutral finish to any kitchen, bathroom, laundry room and more.<br/><br/>Designed to make the cleaning up dry messes quickly and efficiently, Beille’s modern, stylish and functional dust pan and brush set will be a welcomed addition to any home.<br/><br/>CARE: Easily rinse with soap and warm water and pat dry; to maximize longevity, avoid submerging bamboo in water for long periods of time",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
